    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it's not just the strength... the name is literally \"WE_SRV_WATCHING_YOU\". that's not a coincidence. i don't think it's just interference. i think they're using the signal strength or something in the router to actually track my movement in the house. like, it gets maxed out exactly when i'm in the kitchen. how would they even do that if they weren't trying to monitor me?",
